Class ConfigSlice.Filter

All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<ContentName>, Iterable<byte[]>, XMLEncodable, ContentNameProvider
Enclosing class:
ConfigSlice
public static class ConfigSlice.Filter
extends ContentName

Config slice lists require a ConfigSliceOp written before the ContentName, although it does nothing. This class encodes and decodes the preceding ConfigSliceOp and the ContentName together, representing a single filter element.
